UniCredit May Cut Dividend, Capping Rights Offer, Corriere Says

-- B y   S o n i a   S i r l e t t i
-- 
2011-09-20T06:06:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/unicredit-may-cut-dividend-capping-rights-offer-corriere-says.html
UniCredit SpA (UCG)  is considering a
dividend cut to limit the amount of fresh capital it will have
to seek from investors,  Corriere della Sera  reported, without
saying how it obtained the information.  UniCredit needs to raise 4 billion euros to 5 billion
euros, according to the Italian newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sonia Sirletti in Milan at 
 ssirletti@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at 
 fconnelly@bloomberg.net  